title: 已经安装经济插件但是其他需要经济插件的都读取不到是为什么
author: Maple_Lemon
txt_content:
cmi插件给的提示
[CMI] Vault was found but economy engine is missing. Use one from list provided in https://dev.bukkit.org/bukkit-plugins/vault/
Vault was found but not economy plugin, you will have limited economy support

mailbox也提示没安装
-----前置插件[Vault]未安装，已关闭相关功能

其他需要经济前置的都提示没有,但实际已经安装了

replies.author: 远远困了
replies.txt_content:
CMIinjector
装了吗..
或者更新到最新版本的vault

replies.author: 深拥v
replies.txt_content: 是不是vault版本太低了（应该不会吧。。。。）

replies.author: 蕾米洛伊
replies.txt_content:
> Vault was found but economy engine is missing.
有没有安装一个实际的经济插件呢, 比如 Fe 或者 AConomy 之类实际提供经济功能的插件。
或者尝试重新下载安装一个 vault。
